Privacy Policy and Legal Notes

Correios Privacy Policy and Legal Notes

Definitions

Cookie: English term used to designate a file stored in browsers to facilitate their identification. Much used by website database to customize routines for each Internet user;
IP:Internet Protocol is the Internet protocol that identifies, locates and establishes a connection between computers connected to the Internet;
URL: stands for Uniform Resource Location, which is the standard for address names on the Internet. Each page should have its own URL for easy access;
Portal: Set of sites with information on different online and conventional products and services comprising a single environment. The Correios Portal address on the Internet is:www.correios.com.br which covers institutional content, online services and CorreiosNet services;
Sítio:Information available on the Internet by individuals, institutions, companies etc., which belongs to the same address (URL) and generally deals with a specific subject.
